consolerdp (1.0.3) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Fully automated RDP setup: install.sh now provisions everything
    needed for mstsc to work on first connect, no manual KCM step
    required.  consolerdp-configure step 7/8 now:
      - generates a self-signed RSA-2048 TLS cert (10-year validity)
        in ~/.local/share/krdpserver/ if missing,
      - writes ~/.config/krdpserverrc with SystemUserEnabled=true so
        the patched krdp uses PAM for auth (Linux password = RDP
        password),
      - enable-linger's the seat user so the user manager survives
        reboots,
      - enables and starts app-org.kde.krdpserver.service.
  * install.sh adds 'openssl' to APT_PACKAGES (needed for cert gen,
    already present on stock Kubuntu but pinning it for minimal
    images).
  * INSTALL.md updated to document the new "What gets configured"
    list and remove the manual System Settings step.

 -- ConsoleRDP <consolerdp@local>  Mon, 04 May 2026 12:08:00 +0000

consolerdp (1.0.2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Bug fix: install.sh no longer asks apt to install
    `plasma-remotedesktop`, which does not exist on Kubuntu 26.04 /
    Plasma 6. The System Settings RDP KCM (kcm_krdpserver.so) ships
    inside the patched krdp .deb itself, so no separate package is
    needed. (Plasma-5-era leftover.)
  * Removed the same `plasma-remotedesktop` Recommends from the
    consolerdp .deb's debian/control.
  * Updated INSTALL.md accordingly.

 -- ConsoleRDP <consolerdp@local>  Mon, 04 May 2026 11:35:00 +0000

consolerdp (1.0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * install.sh and install-remote.sh now reattach stdin to /dev/tty
    when invoked via `curl ... | sudo bash`, so prompts work even when
    the original stdin is the curl pipe.
  * Added a clearer "ConsoleRDP bootstrap" banner in install-remote.sh
    so the user knows when the script has started.
  * Recommended install pattern in INSTALL.md changed from
    `curl | sudo bash` to "download then sudo bash <file>" because the
    pipe pattern silently broke prompts on some terminals.

 -- ConsoleRDP <consolerdp@local>  Mon, 04 May 2026 10:50:00 +0000

consolerdp (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Orchestrator daemon (consolerdp-daemon) with rdp-watcher disconnect
    debouncing and session auto-unlock on takeover.
  * Helper scripts: claim-screen, corral-windows, isolate-krdp-output,
    output, make-rdp, doctor, takeover/release/ctl, session-watcher.
  * systemd units: consolerdp.service, consolerdp-greeter@.service,
    user-level consolerdp-session-watcher.service.
  * Works with patched krdp and kpipewire (shipped as companion .debs).
  * Target: Kubuntu 26.04 LTS amd64, Plasma 6.6 Wayland.

 -- ConsoleRDP <consolerdp@local>  Mon, 04 May 2026 09:50:00 -0500
